name: "IL BAGATTO"
description:
Here I begin, 
on my table everything I need, on my hands still little experience
First, the beginning, the inexperience and the enthusiasm 
The perspective takes on dimension 
Body and mind get to work
.
.
.
This card is part of an original tarot deck made by Rahtattoo. 
The 22 works that compose it are the result of the study of the ancient symbolism that animates the tarot's major arcana.
